<i>♪ I think it's time for a new adaption ♪</i>

27:50.293 --> 27:54.381
<i>♪ Just get in line and, baby</i>
<i>We've got options ♪</i>

27:54.464 --> 27:58.051
<i>♪ Someone to like you</i>
<i>Something to wear ♪</i>

27:58.134 --> 28:01.679
<i>♪ Somebody to believe you</i>
<i>With everyone, everywhere ♪</i>

28:02.430 --> 28:06.226
<i>♪ It's a condition</i>
<i>And that's my business ♪</i>

28:06.309 --> 28:10.063
<i>♪ You had suspicion but I got promise ♪</i>

28:10.146 --> 28:14.192
<i>♪ Get some freedom ♪</i>

28:15.151 --> 28:18.071
<i>♪ Whatever you want</i>
<i>Together we're in formation ♪</i>

28:18.154 --> 28:21.950
